{"type": "article", "id": 56086, "title": "一款会“悬浮”的背包，可减低因负重对身体造成的压力｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-04T22:59:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47964, "name": "Warm Nordic"}, {"id": 52512, "name": "Piamundo"}, {"id": 2999, "name": "Aesop"}, {"id": 52513, "name": "Bompas＆Parr"}, {"id": 52514, "name": "Tuft + Paw"}, {"id": 52515, "name": "Lightning Packs"}, {"id": 52516, "name": "Isabel Ahm"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 345, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180904224054zbO2FqP7ZC1rT0yp.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Hoverglide – World's 1st “floating” Backpack</h3><p>出远门总希望可以装备充足，但背太多东西行路又会很累，甚至对肩颈造成损害。最近，美国公司 Lightning Packs 便设计了会“悬浮”的背包 HoverGlide，据称，这款背包用了专利技术，可减低因负重对身体造成的压力。</p><p>HoverGlide 用了革命性的专利技术 Suspended Load Technology 和双框架和滑轮系统设计。背包有如坐在铁轨上，有松紧带和滑轮帮助它保持平稳，使背包如悬空般稳定不摇晃，能有效减低人们负重移动时承受的压力。HoverGlide 在步行时可减少冲力达 82%，而在跑步时则可减少冲力达 86%。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224133GV6XA0jSYQwePgoD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655257\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224134il9yL8WXvRomqgzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224133tWNqdOJvwIaCDSzH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224135YEq3c17LZP5TVy9n.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.hot-newtech.com/hoverglide\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lightning Packs</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Milo by Tuft + Paw</h3><p>美国公司 Tuft + Paw 推出名为 Milo 的猫家具，出自设计师 Sang Nam Park 之手。Milo 外观简洁利落，主要材质使用了桦木合板和 UV 固化涂层，以及耐抓耐磨的地毯材质，虽然是不算小件的猫咪家具，但是摆放在家里却也不显得突兀。</p><p>集多功能于一身的 Milo 猫跳台，可以让猫充分在这个小家具上玩耍活动，保持身心健康。Milo 的功能包含有两个猫跳台、两个休息台、滑梯猫抓板、猫抓柱和半圆形透明盆。售价 949 美元，<a href=\"https://www.tuftandpaw.com/collections/cat-trees/products/milo-cat-tree\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224240b3UiEYDKwGRycvFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224241mJXCMZzjbRLA6cID.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224242v5qDWR4yur8jQ32x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.848985\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224243Ed3cefRGjzglPOA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224243vASYTGsgC4602U1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.tuftandpaw.com/collections/cat-trees/products/milo-cat-tree\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tuft + Paw</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>World's First Non-melting Ice Lolly by Bompas＆Parr</h3><p>食品设计工作室 Bompas＆Parr 推出了世界上第一款不会融化的冰棒，配方灵感来自于第二次世界大战期间发明的冷冻复合材料。虽然这个冰棒最终也会融化，但与传统的冰棒不同，这个冰棒能够顶住 24 度的温度，保持不融化一小时。</p><p>设计团队说，设计这个冰棒的初衷是考虑到全球变暖，随着温度的升高，人们越来越喜欢吃冷饮。他们改进了一种用于超强冰的老配方，这种配方最初由英国发明家 Geoffrey Pyke 在第二次世界大战期间帮助武装部队开发的。Bompas＆Parr 用水果纤维代替了 Pyke 使用的锯末和木浆，并把材料做成了冰棒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p07764hj45o\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224326tNfSKvpx4W7Cdcr6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767019\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224327uRECj3pU6tS1LbIT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590948\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224330GUS5FvzWIMH3P27l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Bompas＆Parr</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Imaginative Oil Diffusers and Wash Bags by ÉCAL Students for Aesop</h3><p>澳洲护肤品牌 Aesop 的包装美学早已笼络了大批粉丝。最近，瑞士洛桑艺术设计大学的 17 名毕业生，根据 Aesop 产品量身制作，设计了一套专用配件。Aesop 要求其配件设计必须具备美观、富有创意和可持续三个条件，最终的成品是收纳包与香薰炉。</p><p>其中一款是 Oubadah Nouktah 的玻璃扩香器，外型模仿传统的 Aesop 瓶子。Clavier Margo 的作品，则是香薰制成的半圆形软木陀螺，让精油香气随着缓缓旋动而扩散。收纳包则是延续了 Aesop 朴实低调的风格，能将一切收纳得井井有条。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224412CuojK9VsXHRUxpZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224412qURdKOE2am8e7GMN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809042244130iGMEUkT536hBz8J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018090422441594aBSWUTgv0tZRYb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224415hrmqU8DG4escVIT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224416NG1oMVjzqF8te6ly.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/08/19/aesop-ecal-students-oil-diffusers-wash-bags/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Volcanic Rock Collection by Piamundo</h3><p>设计品牌 Piamundo 推出由火山岩制成的餐具 Volcanic Rock 系列，均采用墨西哥普埃布拉州的石头雕刻而成，用于制作盛装鳄梨酱、玉米饼等墨西哥小吃的餐盘碗具。</p><p>整个系列包括一个浅圆盘，侧面有一个小方形手柄，可用作水果碗。另有两个尺寸更大的碗，其中一个带有加勒比胡桃木制成的盖子，有助于帮助食物保温。除了餐具外，该系列还包括花瓶，每个都有不同的雕塑形式，以突出岩石的质地。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224458q0xAfT2pNO1sFGrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809042245004vOmKgx5bXFaAhkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224500e4YzQr7libLaJ6U5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224501bdhRK4woUQCSruIs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756768\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224501cHWLJYCvQDUZ0ajX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.811760\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224502QKeYyXZjTUcsS6Mq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224502nbqErXdksTxCieS5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rúna Table by Isabel Ahm for Warm Nordic</h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 Warm Nordic 推出一款名为 Rúna 的桌子，出自丹麦设计师 Isabel Ahm 之手。Rúna 的样式颇为复古，是基于 1950 年代北欧木质家具的精髓而做。这款实木桌提供两种尺寸，以及烟熏橡木、柚木和胡桃木三种材质可选。</p><p>它的桌面采用厚实、轻柔弯曲的底面，由四条锥形腿支撑。桌面下方隐藏着小巧的抽屉，可用于存放办公用品、纸张和信件，或放置垫子和餐巾纸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018090422452956jPRE4LV0GHu1ps.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224533qVL5d0G7AnJrCSoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224533EH4C8PgQSl216LW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737310\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224533HSuG9T1tDadUR8w5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180904224536jltd7wuV9N6kLReS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.warmnordic.com/en/categories/mobler\" rel=\"nofollow\">Warm Nordic</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}